### Create user with validation error (duplicate email)
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Another",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "username": "anotheruser",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-12-01T00:00:00Z"
